            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR5c0057-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-14T19:34:08.748+09:00">Out of Tao, One is born;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-14T19:34:17.85+09:00">Out of One, Two;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-14T19:34:26.668+09:00">Out of Two, Three;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-14T19:34:40.675+09:00">Out of Three the created universe.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-14T19:34:56.446+09:00">The created universe carris the yin at its back</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-14T19:35:05.233+09:00">and the yang in front;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-14T19:35:21.658+09:00">Through the union of the pervading principles it reaches harmony.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-14T19:35:59.229+09:00">To be "orphaned", "lonely" and "unworthy" is what men hate most,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-14T19:36:26.378+09:00">Yet the princes and dukes call themselves by such names</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-14T19:36:39.871+09:00">For sometimes things are benefited by being taken away from,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-14T19:36:54.888+09:00">and they suffer by being added to.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-14T19:37:08.571+09:00">Others have taught this maxim,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-14T19:37:17.457+09:00">Which I shall teach also:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-14T19:37:56.599+09:00">"The violent man</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-14T19:38:01.303+09:00">shall die a violent death."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-14T19:38:23.092+09:00">This I regard as my spiritual teacher.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-17T17:48:39.176+09:00">The Tao that can be told of</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.3-h" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-17T17:48:20.593+09:00">1. ON THE ABSOLUTE TAO</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-17T17:48:48.263+09:00">Is not the Absolute Tao;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-17T17:48:56.879+09:00">The Names that can be given</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-17T17:49:03.812+09:00">Are not Absolute Names.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-17T17:49:14.761+09:00">The Nameless is the origin of Heaven and Earth;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-17T17:49:23.698+09:00">The Named is the Mother of All Things.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-19T02:35:48.6+09:00">Therefore Oftentimes, one strips oneself of passion In order to see the Secret of Life;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-17T17:49:49.32+09:00">Oftentimes, one regards life with passion,In order to see its manifest forms.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-19T02:36:33.023+09:00">These two (the Secret and its manifestations) Are (in their nature) the same; They are given different names When they become manifest.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-19T02:36:22.695+09:00">They may both be called the Cosmic Mystery :</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-17T17:50:49.169+09:00">Reaching from the Mystery into the Deeper Mystery</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-17T17:50:55.939+09:00">Is the Gate to the Secret of All Life.</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
